  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/575360/extras/11e4b1f82c680466dce0bea221373d67.avif?t=1532689832\" width=364 height=78 /></span><br><br>A magical 2-d shooter/defender. <br><br>You play as a magus with a wide range of spells to unlock. <br>Your goal is to not let any bad guys pass by using any magical means necessary. <br><br>Take the challenge; Face countless hordes of monsters; defeat the evil bosses; rank up and become Ultimagus!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features include:</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>20 unique spells<br></li><li>Magical trinkets<br></li><li>Choose your way of fighting by creating combinations of spells<br></li><li>50 Levels of increasing difficulty <br></li><li>4 Evil bosses<br></li><li>Progress as a mage with 26 grades<br></li><li>Survival mode<br></li><li>Hours of challenging gameplay</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/575360/extras/0f7c47a57e46ade9f9e8aa45e029f092.webp?t=1532689832\" width=580 height=28 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/575360/extras/db48bbebeb903a03589ca13836d6dd77.avif?t=1532689832\" width=303 height=66 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/575360/extras/c10639fa3698ae67bb04df61dad42479.avif?t=1532689832\" width=616 height=108 /></span>",
